    <p>I've been a Product Designer for <strong>9+ years</strong>. Currently, I'm at <strong>Rover</strong>, where I work on the sitter side of the marketplace — from search and retention to alternative monetization models. My favourite problems live on the supply side: building tools that sitters, couriers, and operators use every day to run their business.</p>
